# Daily internal update: prices + FX -> internal snapshot -> monthly/material
# strategic promotion. Two runs: 06:15 UTC (after US close — settled previous
# EU closes) and 07:45 UTC (after Xetra/Euronext open at 07:00 — Yahoo's daily
# bar rolls to today, so the home's price freshness shows the same day). The
# route is idempotent; the second run refreshes market_prices and the live
# home view while the day's internal snapshot stays deduped. The cron
# container shares the tailscale netns, so 127.0.0.1:3222 is the app itself.
15 6 * * * wget -qO- http://127.0.0.1:3222/api/cron/daily || echo "cfo daily update failed"
45 7 * * * wget -qO- http://127.0.0.1:3222/api/cron/daily || echo "cfo daily update failed"

# Monthly review (Phase 5): the scheduled analyst — reassurance digest,
# regulatory watch, tax-table re-verification. 1st of the month, after that
# day's daily update has run. Re-hits are no-ops (one review per month).
45 6 1 * * wget -qO- http://127.0.0.1:3222/api/cron/review || echo "cfo monthly review failed"
